721601f-a.text:
Manhattan Avenue, north from W. 113th Street. To the left is a triangular park at the convergence of this thoroughfare and Morningside Avenue, same begining here. The Monterey is the 7 story apartment house seen beyond same and nears No. 351 W. 114th Street. Note the gas lamps at the right and the electric fixture at the left.
June 1906.

Geo. L. Balgue
